{"name":"Mirror Image","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This spell creates illusionary doubles of the caster, which mimic his actions exactly. They appear in the space directly around him and distract opponents, who tend to strike the mirror images instead of the caster. More powerful castings can create duplicates of allies or objects. The total number of doubles the caster can create of himself, allies, or objects cannot exceed his Int score.</p><br><p><strong>Spell Data:</strong> @Compendium[dcc-core-book.dcc-core-spell-journals.Mirror Image]{Mirror Image}</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","summary":""},"source":"","config":{"inheritSpellCheck":true},"available":true,"level":2,"range":"Self or touch","duration":"1 round or longer","page":"182","castingTime":"1 round","results":{"table":"Mirror Image","collection":"dcc-core-book.dcc-core-spell-tables-wizard"},"save":"Will vs. spell check DC","spellCheck":{"die":"1d20","value":0},"mercurialEffect":{"value":null,"summary":"","description":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/mirror-mirror.svg","effects":[],"_id":"yzcohQfFatK8CQQQ"}
